data.description: Perched on a hill to take advantage of the view of surrounding hills nearby is this well maintained 4 bedroom 3 bath Lindal Cedar  home. Consisting of over 2800 sq ft of living space, this 3 levels of living space is perfect for any large family looking to have their own private space. Each level has a full bathroom for convenience. A large detached garage has plenty of space for your golf cart or boat as it is just minutes from the golf course and the lake.  Information deemed reliable but not guaranteed, buyer to verify.
